snippet.title: Age of Empires II DE - E3 2019 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition releases 2019 and will be available with Xbox Game Pass for PC. 

Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition celebrates the 20th anniversary of one of the most popular strategy games ever with stunning 4K Ultra HD graphics, remastered audio and a whole new campaign - The Last Khans. Return to Reign in 2019.

Learn more: https://www.xbox.com/games/age-of-empires-II-definitive-edition
